<milestone unit="sentence" n="341" /> <persName n="McPherson,,James,B.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00136" reg="default:McPherson,James,B.,," authname="mcpherson,james,b."><foreName full="yes">James</foreName> <foreName full="yes">B.</foreName> <surname full="yes">McPherson</surname></persName> to be <rs type="role">Lieut.</rs>-<placeName reg="Colorado" key="tgn,7007158" authname="tgn,7007158">Col.</placeName>, to report to <persName n="Halleck,General,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00137" reg="nearbymention:Halleck,A.,J.,," authname="halleck,a.,j."><roleName n="General" full="yes">Gen.</roleName> <surname full="yes">Halleck</surname></persName>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="342" /> The following Assistant Inspectors General have been appointed with the rank of <rs type="role2">Major</rs>: </p> 
